[{"id": 575300, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1708, "text": "A. L. M. R. Bu (harfler), kitab\u0131n mucizeleridir. Rabbinden sana indirilen, ger\u00e7ektir; fakat halk\u0131n \u00e7o\u011fu inanmaz."}, {"id": 575301, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1709, "text": "G\u00f6rebilece\u011finiz bir direk olmadan g\u00f6kleri y\u00fckselten, sonra t\u00fcm y\u00f6netime egemen olan, g\u00fcne\u015fi ve ay\u0131 buyruk alt\u0131na alan ALLAH't\u0131r. Hepsi belli bir s\u00fcre i\u00e7in ak\u0131p gitmektedir. T\u00fcm i\u015fleri kontrol eder ve ayetleri detayl\u0131 olarak a\u00e7\u0131klar ki Rabbinizle kavu\u015fma konusunda ku\u015fkunuz kalmas\u0131n"}, {"id": 575302, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1710, "text": "O ki yery\u00fcz\u00fcn\u00fc in\u015fa edip \u00fczerine sa\u011flam da\u011flar, \u0131rmaklar ve erkekli di\u015fili yaratt\u0131\u011f\u0131 her \u00e7e\u015fit meyveyi yerle\u015ftirdi. Geceyi g\u00fcnd\u00fcze b\u00fcr\u00fcyor. D\u00fc\u015f\u00fcnen bir toplum i\u00e7in elbette bunda i\u015faretler ve dersler vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 575303, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1711, "text": "Yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde, birbirine kom\u015fu toprak par\u00e7alar\u0131, \u00fcz\u00fcm ba\u011flar\u0131, ekinler, \u00e7atall\u0131 ve \u00e7atals\u0131z hurmal\u0131klar vard\u0131r. Bunlar\u0131n hepsi ayn\u0131 su ile sulanmalar\u0131na ra\u011fmen lezzet\u00e7e birbirinden farkl\u0131 k\u0131lm\u0131\u015f\u0131zd\u0131r. Akl\u0131n\u0131 kullanan bir toplum i\u00e7in elbette bunda i\u015faretler ve dersler vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 575304, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1712, "text": "\u015ea\u015facaksan, onlar\u0131n \u015fu s\u00f6zlerine \u015fa\u015fmal\u0131s\u0131n: \"Biz toprak olduktan sonra yeniden mi yarat\u0131laca\u011f\u0131z?\" \u0130\u015fte onlar, Rab'lerini inkar edenlerdir. Onlar, boyunlar\u0131na prangalar hakedenlerdir. Onlar ate\u015fin halk\u0131d\u0131r; nitekim orada ebedi kal\u0131c\u0131d\u0131rlar."}, {"id": 575305, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1713, "text": "\u0130yilik isteyeceklerine, ba\u015flar\u0131na hemen bir felaket getirmeni isterler; oysa kendilerinden \u00f6nce \u00f6rnekler gelip ge\u00e7ti. Rabbin, i\u015fledikleri zulme ra\u011fmen halka kar\u015f\u0131 ba\u011f\u0131\u015flay\u0131c\u0131d\u0131r. Rabbinin azab\u0131 \u00e7etindir."}, {"id": 575306, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1714, "text": "\u0130nkarc\u0131lar, \"Ona bir mucize inmeli de\u011fil miydi,\" diyorlar. Sen ancak bir uyar\u0131c\u0131s\u0131n. Her toplum i\u00e7in bir Yol G\u00f6sterici vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 575307, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1715, "text": "ALLAH her di\u015finin y\u00fcklendi\u011fini, rahimlerin eksiltti\u011fini ve artt\u0131rd\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 bilir. O'nun yan\u0131nda her \u015fey belli bir \u00f6l\u00e7\u00fcye g\u00f6redir."}, {"id": 575308, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1716, "text": "Gizliyi ve a\u00e7\u0131\u011f\u0131 Bilendir; B\u00fcy\u00fckt\u00fcr, Y\u00fccedir."}, {"id": 575309, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1717, "text": "S\u00f6z\u00fc ister gizleyin, ister a\u00e7\u0131klay\u0131n, ister gecenin karanl\u0131\u011f\u0131nda saklan\u0131n, ister g\u00fcnd\u00fcz\u00fcn ortaya \u00e7\u0131k\u0131n O'nun i\u00e7in birdir."}, {"id": 575310, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1718, "text": "(Onlar\u0131n herbiri i\u00e7in) \u00f6n\u00fcnden ve ard\u0131ndan n\u00f6betle\u015ferek izleyenler vard\u0131r. Onu ALLAH'\u0131n emriyle korurlar. Bir topluluk kendisini de\u011fi\u015ftirmedik\u00e7e ALLAH onlar\u0131n durumunu de\u011fi\u015ftirmez. ALLAH bir topluluk i\u00e7in fenal\u0131k istedi mi, hi\u00e7 bir g\u00fc\u00e7 onu durduramaz; onlar\u0131n O'ndan ba\u015fka bir koruyup kollayanlar\u0131 da olmaz."}, {"id": 575311, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1719, "text": "O, size korku ve umut olarak \u015fim\u015fe\u011fi g\u00f6steren ve a\u011f\u0131r bulutlar\u0131 olu\u015fturand\u0131r."}, {"id": 575312, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1720, "text": "G\u00f6k g\u00fcrlemesi O'nu \u00f6verek, melekler de O'nu sayg\u0131yla y\u00fcceltirler. O, y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131mlar\u0131 g\u00f6nderir ve diledi\u011fini onlarla \u00e7arpar. Onlar h\u00e2l\u00e2 ALLAH hakk\u0131nda tart\u0131\u015f\u0131yorlar. O, dayan\u0131lmaz g\u00fcce sahiptir."}, {"id": 575313, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1721, "text": "Ger\u00e7ek dua O'na y\u00f6neltilendir. O'nun d\u0131\u015f\u0131nda \u00e7a\u011f\u0131rd\u0131klar\u0131 ise onlara hi\u00e7 bir \u015fekilde kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k veremezler. T\u0131pk\u0131 suya avu\u00e7lar\u0131n\u0131 uzatan; ancak a\u011fz\u0131na hi\u00e7 bir \u015fey ula\u015fm\u0131yan kimse gibi... \u0130nkarc\u0131lar\u0131n duas\u0131 bo\u015funad\u0131r."}, {"id": 575314, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": true, "sajda_id": 2, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": true, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1722, "text": "G\u00f6klerde ve yerde olan herkes ister istemez ALLAH'a secde eder. G\u00f6lgeleri de sabah ak\u015fam..."}, {"id": 575315, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1723, "text": "De ki: \"G\u00f6klerin ve yerin Rabbi kim?\" De ki: \"ALLAH\" De ki: \"O'ndan ba\u015fka, kendilerine dahi yarar ve zarar veremiyen kimseleri evliyalar m\u0131 edindiniz?\" De ki: \"Hi\u00e7 k\u00f6rle g\u00f6ren bir olur mu, yahut hi\u00e7 karanl\u0131kla \u0131\u015f\u0131k bir olur mu?\" Yoksa ALLAH'\u0131n yaratt\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi yaratan ortaklar buldular da yaratmalar\u0131n\u0131 birbiriyle mi kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131lar? De ki: \"ALLAH her \u015feyin yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131d\u0131r, O Tektir, Egemendir.\""}, {"id": 575316, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1724, "text": "G\u00f6kten bir su indirir, dereler onunla dolar ta\u015far ve sel bol k\u00f6p\u00fck y\u00fcklenir. Ayn\u0131 \u015fekilde, m\u00fccevherat yahut e\u015fya yapmak i\u00e7in erittikleri maddelerden de benzer bir k\u00f6p\u00fck elde ederler. ALLAH ger\u00e7e\u011fi ve bat\u0131l\u0131 b\u00f6yle bir \u00f6rnekle tan\u0131t\u0131r. K\u00f6p\u00fck, kaybolup gider; ancak insanlara yarar veren ise yerde kal\u0131r. \u0130\u015fte ALLAH \u00f6rnekleri b\u00f6yle verir."}, {"id": 575317, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1725, "text": "Rab'lerinin \u00e7a\u011fr\u0131s\u0131na uyanlar g\u00fczeli hak ederler. O'nun \u00e7a\u011fr\u0131s\u0131na uymayanlar ise, yery\u00fcz\u00fcndekilerin hepsine ve bir o kadar\u0131na sahip olsalar dahi kurtulmak i\u00e7in hepsini fidye olarak vermeye haz\u0131r olacaklard\u0131r. Sorgulaman\u0131n en k\u00f6t\u00fcs\u00fc onlar i\u00e7indir ve yerleri cehennemdir; ne de felaketli bir konakt\u0131r o!"}, {"id": 575318, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1726, "text": "Sana indirilenin ger\u00e7ek oldu\u011funu bilen biri, g\u00f6rmeyen gibi midir? Ancak ak\u0131l sahipleri \u00f6\u011f\u00fct al\u0131r."}, {"id": 575319, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1727, "text": "Onlar ki ALLAH'a verdikleri s\u00f6z\u00fc yerine getirirler ve s\u00f6zle\u015fmeyi bozmazlar."}, {"id": 575320, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1728, "text": "Onlar ki ALLAH'\u0131n birle\u015ftirmesini emretti\u011fi \u015feyi birle\u015ftirirler, Rab'lerini sayarlar ve k\u00f6t\u00fc hesaptan korkarlar."}, {"id": 575321, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1729, "text": "Ve onlar ki sadece Rab'lerinin onay\u0131n\u0131 kazanmak i\u00e7in sabredip direnirler, namaz\u0131 g\u00f6zetirler, kendilerine verdi\u011fimiz r\u0131z\u0131klardan gizli ve a\u00e7\u0131k yard\u0131m i\u00e7in harcarlar ve k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fc\u011f\u00fc iyilik ile savarlar. Son dura\u011f\u0131 onlar hak etmi\u015flerdir."}, {"id": 575322, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1730, "text": "Adn cennetlerine girerler. Atalar\u0131ndan, e\u015flerinden ve soylar\u0131ndan iyi olanlar da onunla beraberdir. Melekler de her kap\u0131dan yanlar\u0131na var\u0131rlar."}, {"id": 575323, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1731, "text": "\"Sabretti\u011finizden \u00f6t\u00fcr\u00fc selam (bar\u0131\u015f ve huzur) size olsun. Bu ne g\u00fczel son durak!\""}, {"id": 575324, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1732, "text": "ALLAH'a verdikleri s\u00f6zden sonra s\u00f6zle\u015fmeyi bozanlar, ALLAH'\u0131n birle\u015ftirmeyi emretti\u011fini birle\u015ftirmeyenler ve yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde bozgunculuk yapanlar laneti hakketmi\u015flerdir ve onlar i\u00e7in k\u00f6t\u00fc bir sonu\u00e7 vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 575325, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1733, "text": "ALLAH diledi\u011fine r\u0131zk\u0131 a\u00e7ar veya k\u0131sar. Onlar d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131 ile sevindiler, halbuki bu d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131 ahiret ile kar\u015f\u0131la\u015ft\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda bir ge\u00e7imlikten ibarettir."}, {"id": 575326, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1734, "text": "\u0130nkar edenler, \"Ona Rabbinden bir mucize indirilmeli de\u011fil miydi,\" diyorlar. De ki: \"ALLAH dileyeni sapt\u0131r\u0131r ve y\u00f6neleni do\u011fruya ula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r.\""}, {"id": 575327, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1735, "text": "Onlar ki inan\u0131rlar ve kalpleri ALLAH'\u0131 anmakla huzur bulur. Bilesiniz ki, kalpler ALLAH'\u0131 anmakla yat\u0131\u015f\u0131r."}, {"id": 575328, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1736, "text": "\u0130nan\u0131p erdemli bir hayat s\u00fcrenler i\u00e7in m\u00fcjde ve en g\u00fczel d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f yeri vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 575329, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1737, "text": "Daha \u00f6nceki toplumlara oldu\u011fu gibi seni de bu topluma g\u00f6nderdik ki sana vahyetti\u011fimizi onlara okuyas\u0131n, halbuki onlar Rahman'a nank\u00f6rl\u00fck ediyorlar. De ki: \"O'dur benim Rabbim; O'ndan ba\u015fka tanr\u0131 yoktur. O'na g\u00fcvendim; d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f O'nad\u0131r.\""}, {"id": 575330, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1738, "text": "Kendisiyle da\u011flar y\u00fcr\u00fct\u00fclen, yahut yery\u00fcz\u00fc par\u00e7alanan, yahut \u00f6l\u00fcler dirilten bir Kuran olsayd\u0131 bile (onlar yine inanmazd\u0131). T\u00fcm i\u015fler ALLAH'\u0131n kontrol\u00fcndedir. \u0130nananlar h\u00e2l\u00e2 anlamad\u0131lar m\u0131 ki ALLAH dileseydi t\u00fcm insanlar\u0131 do\u011fruya ula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131rd\u0131. \u0130nkar edenler, ALLAH'\u0131n s\u00f6z\u00fc yerine gelinceye kadar yapt\u0131klar\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k olarak ya ba\u015flar\u0131na ya da yak\u0131nlar\u0131na konacak bir felakete u\u011fray\u0131p duracaklard\u0131r. ALLAH s\u00f6z\u00fcnden d\u00f6nmez."}, {"id": 575331, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1739, "text": "Senden \u00f6nceki el\u00e7ilerle de alay edildi. \u0130nkarc\u0131lara f\u0131rsat verdim ve sonunda onlar\u0131 yakalad\u0131m. Sonu\u00e7 nas\u0131ld\u0131?"}, {"id": 575332, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1740, "text": "Herkesin yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 kontrol eden O de\u011fil midir? Buna ra\u011fmen ALLAH'a ortaklar ko\u015ftular. De ki: \"Onlar\u0131 (diledi\u011finiz) isimlerle tan\u0131mlay\u0131n! Siz O'nun yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde bilmedi\u011fi bir \u015feyi mi O'na haber veriyorsunuz, yoksa bo\u015f s\u00f6zler mi uyduruyorsunuz?\" Asl\u0131nda, inkarc\u0131lar\u0131n hileleri kendilerine s\u00fcsl\u00fc g\u00f6sterilir ve b\u00f6ylece yoldan saparlar. ALLAH kimi sapt\u0131r\u0131rsa ona do\u011fruyu g\u00f6sterecek yoktur."}, {"id": 575333, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1741, "text": "Onlar d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131nda azap hakketmi\u015flerdir. Ahiret azab\u0131 ise daha k\u00f6t\u00fcd\u00fcr. Onlar\u0131 ALLAH'tan kimse kurtaramaz."}, {"id": 575334, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1742, "text": "Erdemlilere s\u00f6z verilen cennetin \u00f6rne\u011fi \u015fudur: Alt\u0131ndan \u0131rmaklar akar, yemi\u015fi de s\u00fcreklidir g\u00f6lgesi de. Bu, erdemlilerin sonudur. Kafirlerin sonu ise ate\u015ftir."}, {"id": 575335, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1743, "text": "Kendilerine kitap vermi\u015f olduklar\u0131m\u0131z sana indirilene sevinirler. Baz\u0131 gruplar onun bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 inkar ederler. De ki: \"ALLAH'a kul olmakla ve O'na ortak ko\u015fmamakla emredildim. O'na \u00e7a\u011f\u0131r\u0131r\u0131m ve d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f\u00fcm de O'nad\u0131r.\""}, {"id": 575336, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1744, "text": "B\u00f6ylece onu Arap\u00e7a bir yasa olarak indirdik. Sana gelen bilgiden sonra onlar\u0131n keyfine uyarsan ALLAH'a kar\u015f\u0131 ne bir dostun ne de bir koruyucun olamaz."}, {"id": 575337, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1745, "text": "Senden \u00f6nce el\u00e7iler g\u00f6nderdik ve onlara e\u015fler ve \u00e7ocuklar verdik. ALLAH'\u0131n izni olmadan hi\u00e7 bir el\u00e7i bir mucize getiremez. Her d\u00f6nemin bir yazg\u0131s\u0131 vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 575338, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1746, "text": "ALLAH diledi\u011fini siler, diledi\u011fini b\u0131rak\u0131r. Ana Kitap O'nun yan\u0131ndad\u0131r."}, {"id": 575339, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1747, "text": "Onlara s\u00f6z verilenlerin bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 sana g\u00f6stersek de, senin can\u0131n\u0131 alsak da, sana d\u00fc\u015fen g\u00f6rev bildirmektir. Hesap ise bize d\u00fc\u015fer."}, {"id": 575341, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1748, "text": "Yery\u00fcz\u00fcn\u00fcn u\u00e7lar\u0131ndan eksiltti\u011fimizi g\u00f6rm\u00fcyorlar m\u0131? ALLAH h\u00fck\u00fcm verir ve O'nun h\u00fckm\u00fcn\u00fc izleyip \u00e7evirecek de yoktur. O, en h\u0131zl\u0131 hesapl\u0131yand\u0131r."}, {"id": 575342, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1749, "text": "Onlardan \u00f6ncekiler de d\u00fczenler kurdular; halbuki t\u00fcm d\u00fczenler ALLAH'a aittir. Her ki\u015finin kazand\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 bilir. Kafirler de zaferin kime ait oldu\u011funu bileceklerdir."}, {"id": 575343, "identifier": "tr.yuksel", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 255, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "transelator_en_name": "Edip Y\u00fcksel", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1750, "text": "\u0130nkar edenler, \"Sen bir el\u00e7i de\u011filsin!,\" diyorlar. De ki, \"ALLAH ve kitab\u0131n bilgisine sahip olanlar benimle sizin aran\u0131zda \u015fahit olarak yeter.\""}]